Package com.sonyericsson.extras.liveware.aef.sensor

Provides the classes necessary to create a Smart Extension API Sensor extension.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Sensor.Intents Intents sent between Sensor Extensions and Accessory Host Applications
Sensor.SensorAccuracy Interface used to define constants for sensor accuracy.
Sensor.SensorApiErrorCodes Interface used to define constants for sensor error codes sent from the host application
Sensor.SensorInterruptMode Interface used to define constants for sensor interrupt mode.
Sensor.SensorRates Interface used to define constants for sensor rates.
 

Class Summary
Sensor Sensor API is a part of the Smart Extension APIs Overview The Sensor API is used to send accessory sensor data from a host application to an accessory extension.
 

Package com.sonyericsson.extras.liveware.aef.sensor Description

Provides the classes necessary to create a Smart Extension API Sensor extension. Refer to Sensor for a detailed description of the Sensor API.
